  "detailed_description": "Delve through the Puzzle Dungeon and try to retrieve the fabled Hypercube.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PICK YOUR HERO</h2>Play one of 4 distinct characters, each with their own type of puzzle. The further you adventure into the dungeon, the harder each puzzle becomes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284200/extras/3e107dde611b77081b3d2d1c55afbd44.poster.avif?t=1741007093\" width=614 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284200/extras/3e107dde611b77081b3d2d1c55afbd44.webm?t=1741007093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284200/extras/3e107dde611b77081b3d2d1c55afbd44.mp4?t=1741007093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND LOOT</h2>Upgrade your character with sweet loot.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284200/extras/9ed40eca56e94bbde18a9c3f4d88cba6.poster.avif?t=1741007093\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284200/extras/9ed40eca56e94bbde18a9c3f4d88cba6.webm?t=1741007093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284200/extras/9ed40eca56e94bbde18a9c3f4d88cba6.mp4?t=1741007093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Test your mental arithmetic, language and cognitive abilities while you adventure through the dungeon. <br><br>Puzzle Dungeon is a turn-based dungeon crawler featuring classic roguelike elements: procedurally generated levels, permanent character upgrades, pixel art graphics, and permadeath.",
